%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stage%20Set%20For%2076th%20Republic%20Day%20Parade%20At%20Kartavya%20Path%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndonesian%20President%20Prabowo%20Subianto%20is%20the%20chief%20guest%20at%20the%20Republic%20Day%20parade.%20Some%2010%2C000%20guests%20have%20been%20invited%20to%20see%20it%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20government's%20objective%20to%20increase%20'Jan%20Bhagidari'%20in%20events%20of%20national%20importance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThirty-one%20tableaux%20will%20roll%20down%20Kartavya%20Path%20on%20the%20theme%20'Swarnim%20Bharat%3A%20Virasat%20aur%20Vikas'.%20In%20a%20first%2C%20a%20tri-services%20tableau%20will%20showcase%20the%20spirit%20of%20jointness%20and%20integration%20among%20the%20armed%20forces.%20Cultural%20performances%20by%20at%20least%205%2C000%20artistes%20will%20cover%20the%20entire%20Kartavya%20Path%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20parade%20will%20start%20at%2010.30%20am%20and%20run%20for%20approximately%2090%20minutes.%20The%20ceremony%20will%20begin%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20National%20War%20Memorial%2C%20where%20he%20will%20lead%20the%20nation%20in%20paying%20solemn%20tributes%20to%20fallen%20heroes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20parade%20will%20be%20heralded%20by%20300%20cultural%20artistes%20playing%20'Sare%20Jahan%20Se%20Achha'%20with%20musical%20instruments%20sourced%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20ensemble%20of%20instruments%20includes%20shehnai%2C%20sundari%2C%20nadaswaram%2C%20been%2C%20mashak%20been%2C%20ransingha%20-%20Rajasthan%2C%20flute%2C%20karadi%20majalu%2C%20mohuri%2C%20sankha%2C%20tutari%2C%20dhol%2C%20gong%2C%20nishan%2C%20chang%2C%20tasha%2C%20sambal%2C%20chenda%2C%20idakka%2C%20lezim%2C%20thavil%2C%20gudum%20baza%2C%20talam%20and%20monbah.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20marching%20contingent%20of%20the%20Indonesian%20National%20Armed%20Forces%20comprising%20152%20members%2C%20and%20a%20band%20of%20Indonesia's%20Military%20Academy%20with%20190%20members%20will%20participate%20in%20the%20parade.%20The%20first%20army%20contingent%20leading%20the%20mounted%20column%20will%20be%20of%2061%20Cavalry%2C%20led%20by%20Lt%20Ahaan%20Kumar.%20Raised%20in%201953%2C%20the%2061%20Cavalry%20is%20the%20only%20serving%20Horsed%20Cavalry%20Regiment%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESome%20of%20the%20military%20hardware%20that%20will%20be%20on%20display%20include%20T-90%20(Bhishma)%20tank%2C%20NAG%20missile%20system%20along%20with%20BMP-2%20Sarath%2C%20BrahMos%20cruise%20missile%2C%20Pinaka%20multi-launcher%20rocket%20system%2C%20Akash%20weapon%20system%2C%20light%20specialist%20vehicle%20(Bajrang)%2C%20and%20vehicle%20mounted%20infantry%20mortar%20system%20(Airawat)%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20tri-services%20tableau%20on%20the%20theme%20'Shashakt%20aur%20Surakshit%20Bharat'%20will%20show%20a%20joint%20operations%20room%20facilitating%20networking%20and%20communication%20among%20the%20three%20armed%20services.%20A%20battlefield%20scenario%20will%20be%20shown%20to%20illustrate%20a%20synchronised%20operation%20in%20land%2C%20water%20and%20air%20with%20the%20indigenous%20Arjun%20main%20battle%20tank%2C%20Tejas%20MKII%20fighter%20aircraft%2C%20Advanced%20Light%20Helicopter%2C%20destroyer%20INS%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20and%20a%20remotely%20piloted%20aircraft.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAnother%20highlight%20is%20the%20veterans'%20tableau%20on%20the%20theme%20'Viksit%20Bharat%20ki%20Ore%20Sadaiv%20Agrasar'%2C%20a%20tribute%20to%20the%20unwavering%20spirit%20of%20veterans%2C%20who%20are%20the%20symbols%20of%20discipline%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20unyielding%20dedication.%20Adding%20to%20the%20display%20of%20honour%20will%20be%20veterans%20who%20have%20brought%20glory%20to%20India%20in%20sports.%20Among%20them%20are%20Padma%20Shri%20awardees%20Subedar%20Murlikant%20Petkar%2C%20whose%20story%20inspired%20the%20Bollywood%20film%20Chandu%20Champion%2C%20and%20Honorary%20Captain%20Jitu%20Rai.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERepresenting%20nari%20shakti%20(women%20power)%20will%20be%20veteran%20women%20officers%20from%20all%20the%20three%20services%20-%20Lieutenant%20Colonel%20Ravinderjeet%20Randhawa%2C%20Lieutenant%20Commander%20Mani%20Agarwal%2C%20and%20Flight%20Lieutenant%20Ruchi%20Saha%2C%20showcasing%20the%20pivotal%20role%20of%20women%20in%20shaping%20the%20armed%20forces.%20Among%20the%20contingents%20marching%20down%20Kartavya%20Path%20will%20be%20a%20148-member%20all-women%20marching%20contingent%20of%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%2C%20led%20by%20Assistant%20Commandant%20Aishwarya%20Joy%20M.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20will%20come%20to%20a%20close%20with%20the%20Beating%20Retreat%20ceremony%2C%20held%20every%20year%20on%20January%2029%20at%20Vijay%20Chowk.%20It%20marks%20a%20centuries%20old%20military%20tradition%2C%20when%20troops%20ceased%20fighting%2C%20sheathed%20their%20arms%2C%20withdrew%20from%20the%20battlefield%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20camps%20at%20sunset%20at%20the%20sounding%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bretreat%26quot%3B.%20During%20the%20Beating%20Retreat%20ceremony%202025%2C%20only%20Indian%20tunes%20will%20be%20played%20by%20all%20the%20participating%20bands.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737854280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fljjq12dg_republic-day-2025_625x300_25_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstage-set-for-76th-republic-day-parade-at-kartavya-path-10-points-7559146%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20will%20lead%20the%20nation%20in%20celebrating%20the%2076th%20Republic%20Day%20from%20Delhi's%20Kartavya%20Path%20today.%20With%20special%20focus%20on%2075%20years%20of%20enactment%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20Jan%20Bhagidari%2C%20the%20celebrations%20this%20year%20will%20be%20unique.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22