cans%20hold%20majorities%20in%20both%20chambers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Vice%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharris-agrees-trump-tips-service-workers-not-taxed-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKamala%20Harris%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%202024%20Democratic%20presidential%20nominee%2C%20promoted%20a%20similar%20idea%20during%20her%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20Trump%20said%20he'd%20work%20with%20members%20of%20Congress%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20coming%20weeks%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20a%20bill%20reaches%20his%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20tax%20on%20tips!%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20as%20a%20crowd%20of%20supporters%20cheered%20nearby.%20During%20the%20speech%2C%20Trump%20said%20his%20administration%20would%20also%20raise%20worker%20wages%2C%20but%20did%20not%20share%20additional%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20speech%2C%20Trump%20welcomed%20American%20Hotel%20and%20Lodging%20Association%20CEO%20and%20President%20Rosanna%20Maietta%20onstage%2C%20where%20she%20spoke%20about%20the%20proposal's%20potential%20impact%20on%20the%20service%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20here%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20the%20American%20dream%20is%20alive%20and%20well%20in%20the%20hotel%20industry%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20referenced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tax-reform-plan-analysis-study-rich-rates-2017-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etax%20bill%20Trump%20promoted%20in%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20his%20first%20administration.%20%26quot%3BThe%20'no%20tax%20on%20tips'%20builds%20on%20that%20momentum%2C%26quot%3B%20Maietta%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20we%20are%20so%20excited%20to%20support%20you%20in%20that%20effort.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20her%20organization%20would%20urge%20Congress%20to%20pass%20Trump's%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20however%2C%20Trump's%20remarks%20dr