budgeting%20approach%20could%20be%20a%20valuable%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20newspaper.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20amongst%20the%20people%20who%20think%20the%20deficit%20needs%20to%20be%20brought%20down%20because%20otherwise%2C%20it%20will%20create%20a%20financial%20problem%20for%20us.%20That%20effort%20could%20come%20up%20with%20some%20good%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-doge-department-government-efficiency-creation-elon-musk-executive-order-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20recently%20saw%20the%20departure%20of%20businessman%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20as%20a%20co-lead%2C%20aims%20to%20tackle%20government%20inefficiencies%20and%20reduce%20the%20deficit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20DOGE%20was%20first%20proposed%2C%20Musk%20set%20a%20goal%20to%20cut%20%242%20trillion%20in%20spending.%20However%2C%20during%20a%20conversation%20with%20political%20strategist%20Mark%20Penn%20earlier%20in%20January%2C%20Musk%20said%20the%20%242%20trillion%20figure%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bbest-case%20outcome%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20commission%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%20shot%26quot%3B%20at%20saving%20%241%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDOGE%20announced%20on%20Friday%20that%20it%20had%20canceled%20roughly%20%24420%20million%20worth%20of%20existing%20or%20forthcoming%20contracts%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20two%20leases.%20However%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-doge-early-spending-dei-contracts-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20calculations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20commission%20would%20need%20to%20be%20far%20more%20aggressive%20in%20its%20spending%20cuts%20to%20meet%20any%20of%20its%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20Gates'%20interview%2C%20Journal%20editor%20in%20chief%20Emma%20Tucker%20asked%20the%20Microsoft%20cofounder%20where%20he'd%20look%20to%20find%20savings%20if%20he%20was%20leading%20DO