mories%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225bc83c76-09d2-4748-9dce-5e5b3ed79a4c%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20no%20kids'%20menu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20before%20that%20happened%2C%20the%20trip%20had%20proved%20challenging.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20tourists%20in%20Providencia's%20tiny%20but%20gorgeous%20island%20stay%20at%20locally-owned%20guest%20houses%20or%20hotels%2C%20but%20since%20my%20mom%20had%20lived%20there%20for%20several%20years%2C%20we%20were%20staying%20with%20our%20island%20%26quot%3Bfamily.%26quot%3B%20In%20the%20'90s%2C%20there%20was%20no%20A%2FC%20in%20the%20house%2C%20and%20water%20was%20limited.%20To%20shower%2C%20we%20had%20to%20fill%20buckets%20with%20water%20and%20then%20use%20bowls%20to%20pour%20the%20water%20on%20ourselves.%20I%20was%20used%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-do-in-bogota-colombia-24-hours-visit-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20comforts%20of%20Bogota%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20huge%20capital%20city%20whose%20year-round%2060-degree%20weather%20made%20the%20island%20heat%20difficult%20to%20bear.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20also%20had%20to%20eat%20crab%20soup%20and%20other%20seafood%20I%20didn't%20like.%20We%20ate%20whatever%20was%20at%20the%20house%20%E2%80%94%20no%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-cheap-easy-lunch-ideas-big-family-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ekids'%20menu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20choices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20rather%20than%20ruining%20the%20vacation%20for%20me%2C%20these%20challenges%20made%20it%20memorable.%20This%20has%20convinced%20me%20of%20one%20important%20truth%3A%20Kids%20don't%20always%20need%20to%20be%20comfortable%20while%20traveling.%20Seeing%20my%20mom%20and%20my%20grandma%20seamlessly%20adapt%20to%20the%20circumstances%20without%20complaining%20or%20even%20remarking%20on%20them%20made%20me%20react%20the%20same%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d62acf9-953e-4098-9de9-774d30f6a8b0%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20trip%20helped%20me%20grow%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELiving%20without%20the%20comforts%20of%20the%20city%20and%20trying%20foods%20that%20I%20didn't%20necessarily%20like%20felt%20like%20small%20adventures%20to%20my%20six-year-old%20self.%20These%20experiences%20helped%20me%20build%20a%20sense%20of%20identity%20as%20someone%20adventurous%2C%20flexible%2C%20and%20willing%20to%20step%20out%20of%20her%20comfort%20zone.%20Four%20years%20after%20the%20trip%2C%20this%20identity%20helped%20me%20navigate%20life%20in%20a%20new%20country%20when%20my%20family%20moved%20to%20the%20US.%20It's%20also%20helped%20me%20as%20an%20adult%20as%20I've%20traveled%20to%20over%2045%20countries%20and%20lived%20in%20four%20continents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20the%20very%20painful%20jellyfish%20sting%20(and%20its%20very%20embarrassing%20cure)%20became%20my%20first%20tale%20of%20travel%20misadventure%2C%20which%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20share%20with%20my%20siblings%20when%20I%20returned%20to%20Bogota.%20In%20my%20brain%2C%20these%20challenges%20were%20stored%20in%20the%20same%20place%20as%20the%20good%20memories%20of%20the%20trip%3A%20floating%20in%20the%20Sea%20of%20Seven%20Colors%20next%20to%20my%20grandmother%2C%20falling%20asleep%20in%20a%20hammock%2C%20reading%20with%20my%20mom%20as%20we%20lay%20on%20the%20sand%2C%20and%20being%20on%20an%20island%20that%20truly%20feels%20disconnected%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20As%20a%20whole%2C%20I%20remember%20it%20as%20a%20beautiful%20trip%20with%20two%20of%20the%20people%20that%20I%20loved%20the%20most.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20grandmother%20died%20very%20recently.%20This%20was%20the%20only%20real%20trip%20we%20ever%20went%20on%20together%2C%20and%20I%20am%20now%20more%20grateful%20than%20ever%20for%20those%20hot%2C%20uncomfortable%20nights%20spent%20in%20a%20tiny%20room%20with%20her.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20also%20glad%20that%20the%20jellyfish%20taught%20me%20at%20a%20young%20age%20that%20I%20should%20(almost)%20always%20listen%20to%20her%20wisdom.%20I'm%20sure%20that%20it%20saved%20me%20from%20even%20harsher%20stings%20in%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisastrous-first-trip-as-a-child-my-favorite-memories-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737819362000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793b943ae09223df2bb6063%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisastrous-first-trip-as-a-child-my-favorite-memories-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20mom%20had%20to%20pee%20on%20me%20after%20I%20got%20stung%20by%20a%20jellyfish%20and%20I%20ate%20things%20I%20didn't%20like.%20But%20that%20trip%20made%20me%20adaptable%20and%20adventurous.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mariana%20Zapata)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A74%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisastrous-first-trip-as-a-child-my-favorite-memories-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scammers%20are%20now%20sending%20fake%20toll-collection%20texts%20to%20get%20your%20bank%20information%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20toll%20road%20in%20Atlantic%20Beach%20Bridge%20on%20Long%20Island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793fbf0196626c40984fc27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221602%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EToll%20booths%20at%20Atlantic%20Beach%20Bridge%20on%20Long%20Island.%3Cp%3EJ.%20Conrad%20Williams%2C%20Jr.%2FNewsday%20RM%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAuthorities%20are%20warning%20about%20scam%20texts%20that%20claim%20unpaid%20toll%20fees%20to%20access%20bank%20info.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EScammers%20imitate%20legitimate%20toll%20services%20like%20FastTrak%20and%20EZdriveMA%20to%20deceive%20users.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAvoid%20clicking%20links%20in%20suspicious%20texts%3B%20report%20scams%20to%207726%20to%20protect%20personal%20data.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDid%20you%20get%20a%20text%20saying%20that%20you%20owe%20unpaid%20toll%20fees%3F%20It's%20probably%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-buy-tops-scam-list-microsoft-geek-squad-ftc-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20across%20the%20United%20States%20are%20warning%20about%20a%20wave%20of%20scam%20text%20messages%20that%20claim%20the%20person%20receiving%20the%20message%20has%20unpaid%20fees.%20The%20real%20goal%20of%20the%20scam%20is%20to%20give%20the%20criminals%20access%20to%20your%20bank%20account%20information%2C%20police%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20text%20messages%20are%20the%20latest%20phishing%20scam%20targeting%20victims%20across%20the%20country%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20Attorney%20General%20Rob%20Bonta%20said%20in%20a%20warning%20that%20the%20text%20messages%20usually%20contain%20a%20link%20designed%20to%20%26quot%3Bdeceive%20drivers%20into%20entering%20banking%20or%20credit%20card%20information%20into%20a%20website.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BScammers%20have%20become%20skilled%20at%20imitating%20legitimate%20companies%2C%20sometimes%20even%20linking%20to%20legitimate%20websites%2C%26quot%3B%20Bonta%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BText-based%20toll%20charge%20scams%20are%20prevalent%20right%20now%20and%20knowing%20what%20to%20look%20for%20can%20keep%20consumers%20safe%20against%20these%20tactics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBonta%20said%20that%20scam%20texts%20in%20California%20may%20claim%20to%20come%20from%20the%20state's%20toll%20payment%20service%2C%20FastTrak.%20One%20scam%20text%20message%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20claimed%20to%20be%20from%20Massachusetts'%20EZdriveMA%20toll%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20state%20services%2C%20EZdriveMA%20and%20FastTrak%2C%20say%20they%20do%20not%20send%20text%20messages%20to%20non-account%20holders%20to%20collect%20toll%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20say%20the%20best%20way%20to%20avoid%20becoming%20a%20victim%20of%20these%20fake%20toll%20text%20messages%20is%20not%20to%20click%20on%20the%20link%20provided%20in%20the%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClicking%20on%20the%20link%20could%20expose%20your%20personal%20information%2C%20such%20as%20a%20driver's%20license%20number%2C%20to%20the%20scammers%20and%20put%20you%20at%20risk%20of%20identity%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FTC%20also%20recommends%20checking%20where%20suspicious%20messages%20may%20come%20from%20to%20see%20if%20the%20source%20is%20legitimate%20and%20forward%20scam%20messages%20to%207726%20(SPAM)%20to%20report%20them%20as%20junk%20mail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Better%20Business%20Bureau%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20month%20that%20a%20similar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholiday-scams-learn-how-to-spot-and-avoid-them-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escam%20text%20campaign%20impersonating%20the%20US%20Postal%20Service%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20scams%20the%20organization%20saw%20during%20the%20holiday%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMelanie%20McGovern%2C%20BBB%20director%20of%20public%20relations%2C%20also%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20best%20method%20to%20spot%20a%20phishing%20scam%20is%20to%20check%20from%20where%20the%20text%20or%20email%20came.%20Scam%20text%20messages%20from%20the%20USPS%20scam%20last%20month%20and%20the%20toll%20collection%20scam%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20had