id%20concerns%20about%20immigration%20enforcement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fchicago-elementary-school-mistakes-secret-service-for-ice-agents%2Farticleshow%2F117557789.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fchicago-elementary-school-mistakes-secret-service-for-ice-agents%2Famp_articleshow%2F117557789.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fchicago-elementary-school-mistakes-secret-service-for-ice-agents%2Famp_articleshow%2F117557789.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan%20Reduce%20Financial%20Burden%26quot%3B%3A%20President%20On%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20a%20reform%20that%20will%20%26quot%3Bredefine%20the%20terms%20of%20good%20governance%26quot%3B%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20said%20the%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20bill%20will%20help%20check%20%26quot%3Bpolicy%20paralysis%2C%20mitigate%20resource%20division%2C%20and%20reduce%20financial%20burden%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReforms%20of%20such%20magnitude%20require%20an%20audacity%20of%20vision.%20Another%20measure%20that%20promises%20to%20redefine%20the%20terms%20of%20good%20governance%20is%20the%20Bill%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20to%20synchronise%20election%20schedules%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election'%20plan%20can%20promote%20consistency%20in%20governance%2C%20prevent%20policy%20paralysis%2C%20mitigate%20resource%20diversion%2C%20and%20reduce%20the%20financial%20burden%2C%20apart%20from%20offering%20many%20other%20benefits%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20President%20Murmu%20addressing%20the%20nation%20on%20the%20eve%20of%2076th%20Republic%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20frequently%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20simultaneous%20polls%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20country%20incurs%20significant%20costs%20and%20disruptions%20from%20ongoing%20election%20seasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20president%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20who%20headed%20a%20panel%20on%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election%2C'%20has%20said%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20simultaneous%20polls%20was%20perceived%20by%20the%20framers%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20therefore%20it%20cannot%20be%20unconstitutional.%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20first%20four%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20polls%20were%20held%20together%20till%201967%2C%20asking%20how%20could%20synchronised%20polls%20be%20dubbed%20as%20unconstitutional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20simultaneous%20polls%20idea%20is%20against%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20that%20it%20would%20oppose%20it%20%26quot%3Btooth%20and%20nail%26quot%3B.%20It%20has%20also%20called%20the%20idea%20of%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20anti-democratic%20and%20anti-federal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20syncing%20electoral%20cycles%2C%20there%20is%20no%20real%20clarity%20on%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20breaks%20due%20to%20dissolution%20of%20Houses%2C%20President's%20Rule%2C%20or%20even%20a%20hung%20Assembly%20or%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20emphasised%20the%20government's%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20%26quot%3Beliminate%20remnants%20of%20a%20colonial%20mindset%20that%20have%20lingered%20in%20the%20country%20for%20decades%26quot%3B%20and%20cited%20the%20replacement%20of%20the%20British-era%20criminal%20laws%20with%20three%20new%20modern%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20witnessing%20concerted%20efforts%20to%20change%20that%20mindset...%20Reforms%20of%20such%20magnitude%20require%20an%20audacity%20of%20vision%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20mentioned%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%2C%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Adhiniyam%2C%20which%20prioritise%20the%20delivery%20of%20justice%20over%20mere%20punishment%20and%20place%20a%20strong%20emphasis%20on%20addressing%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20persistently%20high%20economic%20growth%20rate%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20which%20has%20generated%20job%20opportunities%2C%20increased%20income%20for%20farmers%20and%20labourers%2C%20and%20lifted%20many%20out%20of%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20underscored%20the%20importance%20of%20inclusive%20growth%20and%20the%20government's%20commitment%20to%20welfare%2C%20making%20basic%20necessities%20such%20as%20housing%20and%20access%20to%20clean%20drinking%20water%20entitlements%20for%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20to%20support%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20particularly%20those%20belonging%20to%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%2C%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%2C%20were%20also%20highlighted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20highlighted%20the%20inclusive%20nature%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20which%20represented%20diverse%20communities%20across%20the%20nation%2C%20including%2015%20women%20members%20who%20played%20pivotal%20roles%20in%20shaping%20the%20country's%20democratic%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20women's%20equality%20was%20a%20distant%20goal%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20Indian%20women%20were%20actively%20engaged%20in%20the%20nation's%20destiny%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%2C%20according%20to%20the%20President%2C%20has%20evolved%20into%20a%20living%20document%20that%20serves%20as%20the%20foundation%20of%20India's%20collective%20identity%20and%20has%20guided%20the%20nation's%20progress%20over%20the%20past%2075%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20praised%20the%20early%2020th-century%20freedom%20fighters%20for%20uniting%20the%20nation%20in%20a%20well-organised%20independence%20movement%20and%20credited%20iconic%20figures%20like%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%2C%20and%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20for%20helping%20India%20rediscover%20its%20democratic%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJustice%2C%20liberty%2C%20equality%2C%20and%20fraternity%20are%20not%20just%20modern%20concepts%3B%20they%20have%20always%20been%20integral%20to%20our%20civilisational%20heritage%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asserted%2C%20noting%20that%20skeptics%20of%20the%20Constitution's%20future%20were%20proven%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737818640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fa5sd5cng_president-murmu-_625x300_25_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpromises-to-redefine-good-governance-president-murmu-backs-one-nation-one-poll-7557931%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Calling%20it%20a%20reform%20that%20will%20%26quot%3Bredefine%20the%20terms%20of%20good%20governance%26quot%3B%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20said%20the%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20bill%20will%20help%20check%20%26quot%3Bpolicy%20paralysis%2C%20mitigate%20resource%20division%2C%20and%20reduce%20financial%20burden%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Emotional%20reunions%20as%20Israeli%20hostages%20see%20their%20families%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737818130000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fad06%2Flive%2F7e737ff0-db2b-11ef-bc01-8f2c83dad217.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fclyk4xv93e0o%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20female%20IDF%20soldiers%20returned%20to%20Israel%20in%20the%20second%20ceasefire%20hostage%20and%20prisoner%20swap.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engage