20to%20keep%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20all%20of%20them%2C%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20credit%20card%20offered%20five%20alerts%20that%20I%20could%20turn%20on%20for%20protection%20and%20security%20usage.%20One%20alert%20will%20notify%20me%20if%20international%20charges%20have%20been%20posted%20to%20this%20account%3B%20another%20if%20an%20online%2C%20phone%2C%20or%20mail%20charge%20is%20authorized%3B%20and%20one%20that%20will%20alert%20me%20of%20any%20changes%20more%20than%20a%20certain%20dollar%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurning%20these%20on%20gives%20me%20peace%20of%20mind%20that%20alerts%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20me%20via%20email%20and%20text%20if%20there's%20any%20activity%20happening%20on%20the%20card%20that%20requires%20my%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ab851337-b822-4b03-a2a4-b63ea7dd2bcc%5C%22%3E2.%20I%20enabled%20two-factor%20authentication%20for%20my%20credit%20card%20account%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20lazy%20in%20the%20past%20and%20turned%20off%20two-factor%20authentication%20for%20credit%20card%20accounts%20to%20log%20in%20quicker%20and%20see%20my%20balance%20or%20statements.%20I%20went%20to%20each%20of%20my%20accounts%20and%20turned%20on%20two-factor%20authentication.%20Every%20time%20I%20access%20these%20accounts%2C%20a%20code%20is%20sent%20to%20my%20email%20or%20phone%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20help%20prevent%20someone%20from%20accessing%20my%20credit%20card%20accounts%20even%20if%20they%20have%20my%20password%2C%20since%20they%20will%20need%20this%20code%20before%20entering.%20Plus%2C%20if%20I%20receive%20an%20access%20code%20that%20I%20didn't%20request%2C%20this%20will%20alert%20me%20that%20someone%20is%20trying%20to%20break%20into%20my%20credit%20card%20account%2C%20and%20I%20can%20promptly%20change%20my%20password%20and%20alert%20the%20credit%20card%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286d025cd-0a32-4f67-8827-f5fb33e3aceb%5C%22%3E3.%20I%20locked%20my%20credit%20so%20no%20hard%20inquiries%20can%