0of%20those%20set%20for%20release%20was%20published%2C%20our%20world%20collapsed.%20Even%20though%20we%20were%20prepared%20for%20this%20possibility%2C%20we%20had%20hoped%20to%20see%20Shiri%20and%20the%20children%20on%20the%20list%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20for%20civilian%20women.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Israeli%20authorities%20insist%20on%20the%20return%20of%20Kfir%20and%20Ariel%2C%20Hamas%20has%20claimed%20that%20Shiri%20and%20her%20two%20boys%20are%20no%20longer%20alive.%20Israeli%20officials%20have%20not%20confirmed%20this%2C%20and%20the%20uncertainty%20has%20left%20the%20family%20anxious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20analyst%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2025-01-24%2Fbibas-family-fate-has-israelis-holding-their-breath%2F104852460%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20whether%20they're%20alive%20depends%20on%20who%20is%20asked%20about%20it.%20Should%20they%20be%20confirmed%20dead%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20unleash%20fury%20and%20sadness%20in%20Israel%2C%20where%20the%20family%20has%20become%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20country's%20darkest%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20AFP%20report%2C%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20spokesperson%20Daniel%20Hagari%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20concerns%E2%80%9D%20over%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20two%20remaining%20child%20hostages%20from%20the%20Bibas%20family%20in%20Gaza.%20In%20a%20televised%20statement%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Hagari%20said%20that%20Israel%20insists%20on%20the%20return%20of%20Kfir%20and%20Ariel%20Bibas.%20Hagari%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20for%20their%20fate%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20also%20mentioned%20their%20mother%2C%20whose%20deaths%20Hamas%20had%20announced%20more%20than%20a%20year%20ago%20but%20Israeli%20authorities%20have%20not%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20family's%20plea%20remains%20steadfast%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CShir