22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gautam%20Gambhir%C2%A0%20during%20his%20time%20with%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%20He%20scored%20796%20runs%20at%20an%20average%2099.50%20in%20the%202006-07%20Ranji%20Trophy%20season.%20He%20led%20Bengal%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20cricketers%20to%20emerge%20from%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwary%2C%20however%2C%20had%20to%20face%20a%20lot%20of%20struggle%20both%20on%20and%20off%20the%20field.%20He%20even%20thought%20of%20taking%20early%20retirement%20after%20he%20did%20not%20get%20enough%20opportunities%20for%20an%20extended%20period%20in%20the%20Indian%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20responsibility%2C%20I%20did%20not%20take%20early%20retirement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20asked%20on%20his%20struggle%20in%20the%20teenage%20years%20when%20he%20had%20to%20work%20hard%20to%20pay%20off%20loans.%20%26quot%3BThose%20were%20difficult%20times.%20One%20thing%20I%20always%20had%20in%20mind%20was%20that%20I%20had%20to%20pay%20off%20the%20loan.%20We%20have%20%3Cem%3EMangla%20Haat%3C%2Fem%3E%20In%20Kolkata%2C%20there%20I%20used%20to%20sell%20%3Cem%3Epoori%20sabzi%3C%2Fem%3E.%20My%20mom%20used%20to%20make%20the%20pooris.%20Sometimes%20people%20did%20not%20even%20pay%20for%20the%20food%20that%20they%20ate%2C%26quot%3B%20Manoj%20Tiwary%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJfwQ2knqqDo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELallantop%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20worked%20in%20factories%20of%20nut%20and%20bolts.%20This%20was%20around%20when%20I%20was%20around%2014%20years%20old.%20I%20got%20Rs%201200%20per%20match%20when%20I%20played%20in%20U-16%20level.%20So%20I%20did%20the%20maths%20and%20made%20sure%20I%20did%20well%20in%20cricket%20so%20that%20the%20%C2%A0money%20always%20comes.%20I%20ran%20away%20from%20the%20factory.%20It%20was%20too%20hectic.%20The%20factory%20owner%20used%20to%20make%20us%20work.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20his%20debut%20came%20in%202008%20it%20was%20not%20special.%20He%20slammed%20his%20maiden%20ODI%20century%20against%20West%20Indies%20in%20Chennai%20in%202011%2C%20but%20was%20benched%20for%20months%20after%20that%20game.%20MS%20Dhoni%20was%20the%20skipper%20of%20the%20side%20duting%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20the%20captain.%20Team%20India%20runs%20according%20to%20the%20planning%20of%20the%20skipper.%20In%20state%20teams%2C%20things%20are%20different%20but%20in%20Team%20India%20its%20all%20about%20the%20captain.%20If%20you%20see%2C%20during%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kapil%20Dev%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40958-ramlal-nikhanj-kapil-dev-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKapil%20Dev%3C%2Fa%3E's%20time%20it%20was%20he%20who%20ran%20the%20show%2C%20during%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E's%20tenure%20it%20was%20his%20call%2C%20same%20was%20during%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammad%20Azharuddin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40063-mohammad-azizuddin-azharuddin-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Azharuddin%3C%2Fa%3E's%20tenure.%20After%20that%20Dada%20and%20so%20on.%20This%20will%20go%20on%20unless%20a%20strict%20administrator%20comes%20and%20makes%20a%20set%20rule%2C%26quot%3B%20Manoj%20Tiwary%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20see%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajit%20Agarkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F100-ajit-agarkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAjit%20Agarkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20(current%20BCCI%20chief%20selector)%20and%20you%20feel%20he%20can%20take%20strong%20decisions.%20He%20can%20disagree%20with%20the%20coach.%20As%20far%20as%20me%20being%20dropped%20for%2014%20mat