%20instability.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESOF%20missions%20like%20foreign%20internal%20defense%20could%20be%20prudent%2C%20but%20only%20to%20augment%20nonmilitary%20approaches.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20world%20is%20kicking%20around%20the%20idea%20of%20sending%20special%20operations%20forces%20into%20Mexico%20to%20combat%20drug%20cartels.%20There's%20a%20risk%20these%20operations%20could%20make%20things%20worse%2C%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20designating%20Mexican%20cartels%20as%20%26quot%3Bforeign%20terrorist%20organizations%26quot%3B%20on%20Monday%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20asked%20by%20reporters%20whether%20he%20would%20consider%20sending%20US%20special%20operations%20personnel%20to%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCould%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20president%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FCBSNews%2Fstatus%2F1881507323853869270%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20noting%20that%20%26quot%3Bstranger%20things%20have%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20on%20the%20cartels%20and%20warfare%20said%20that%20sending%20any%20military%20troops%20into%20Mexico%20risks%20stirring%20instability%2C%20which%20could%20then%20spill%20over%20the%20border%20into%20US%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20that%20the%20American%20people%20have%20the%20stomach%20for%20what's%20going%20to%20happen%20if%20we%20start%20messing%20around%20down%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20active-duty%20special%20operator%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20speaking%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20because%20he%20wasn't%20authorized%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20throwing%20any%20military%20mechanism%20at%20this%20problem%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20just%20killing%20cartel%20leaders%20is%20not%20going%20to%20change%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20only%20going%20to%20make%20things%20worse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20Green%20Berets%20inside%20a%20building%20with%20gray%20walls%20during%20a%20room-clearing%20exercise.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8a0cec72ebc54a40e485a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221659%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Army%20Green%20Berets%20prepare%20to%20breach%20and%20enter%20a%20building%20as%20part%20of%20Close%20Quarter%20Battle%20training.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%2FStaff%20Sgt.%20Thomas%20Mort%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20floated%20the%20idea%20of%20military%20intervention%20in%20Mexico%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-send-troops-mexico-hunt-drug-cartels-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20his%20first%20term%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20his%20team%20now%20appears%20to%20be%20considering%20the%20idea%20more%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20much%20should%20we%20invade%20Mexico%3F%26quot%3B%20a%20transition%20team%20member%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20250118050248%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.rollingstone.com%2Fpolitics%2Fpolitics-features%2Ftrump-mexico-drug-cartels-military-invade-1235183177%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Rolling%20Stone%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%202024%20for%20a%20report%20on%20Trump's%20musings%20about%20combating%20cartels%20in%20Mexico.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20the%20question.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20new%20national%20security%20advisor%2C%20Mike%20Waltz%2C%20a%20former%20Green%20Beret%2C%20has%20pushed%20the%20idea%20of%20using%20special%20operators.%20And%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bborder%20czar%2C%26quot%3B%20Tom%20Homan%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2Ftranscripts%2Fnx-s1-5187973%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20special%20operations%20forces%20could%20be%20used%20to%20take%20the%20cartels%20out%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Btake%20them%20off%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Earth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDirect%20action%20raids%20%E2%80%94%20hard-hitting%20missions%20US%20special%20operations%20is%20known%20for%20and%20which%20Trump%20appears%20inclined%20to%20pursue%20%E2%80%94%20on%20Mexican%20soil%20would%20bring%20disastrous%20consequences%2C%20especially%20if%20conducted%20without%20an%20invitation%20from%20Mexico%2C%20the%20operator%20and%20other%20experts%20BI%20spoke%20with%20warned.%20But%20other%2C%20less%20kinetic%20missions%2C%20like%20training%20foreign%20troops%20or%20improving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsoaa.org%2Fwhat-is-fid-foreign-internal-defense%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforeign%20internal%20defense%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20could%20prove%20worthwhile%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20missions%20have%20long%20been%20the%20bread%20and%20butter%20of%20forces%20like%20the%20Army's%20Green%20Berets.%20With%20Trump's%20formal%20designation%20of%20cartels%20as%20foreign%20terrorist%20organizations%2C%20those%20kinds%20of%20missions%20could%20augment%20other%20government%20efforts%20to%20more%20effectively%20stem%20the%20flow%20of%20drugs%20into%20the%20US%2C%20sources%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225637c6d0-e919-4587-b844-936446819ff6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20idea%20that%20keeps%20coming%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20using%20special%20operators%20to%20combat%20cartels%20in%20Mexico%20has%20gained%20traction%20among%20leading%20Republicans%2C%20particularly%20military%20veterans.%20Before%20Florida%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%2C%20a%20former%20naval%20officer%2C%20ended%20his%20bid%20for%20the%20White%20House%2C%20he%20told%20CNN%20that%20if%20elected%20president%2C%20he%20would%20deploy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F08%2F26%2Fpolitics%2Fdesantis-special-forces-mexico%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20special%20operations%20forces%20into%20Mexico%20%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3Bon%20day%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Waltz%2C%20then%20a%20congressional%20representative%20from%20Florida%2C%20and%20Dan%20Crenshaw%2C%20a%20Texas%20congressman%20and%20former%20Navy%20SEAL%2C%20introduced%20new%20Authorization%20of%20Military%20Force%20legislation%20aimed%20at%20Mexican%20cartels.%20Such%20legislation%20is%20notably%20not%20often%20quickly%20reversed%20%E2%80%94%20both%20of%20the%20AUMFs%20that%20allowed%20the%20Global%20War%20on%20Terror%20to%20balloon%20in%20scope%20are%20still%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20send%20special%20operations%20forces%20into%20Mexico%20is%20understandable%2C%20said%20Bruce%20Hoffman%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20for%20counterterrorism%20and%20homeland%20security%20at%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations.%20Other%20measures%20have%20failed%20to%20curb%20the%20flow%20of%20drugs%20into%20the%20US%2C%20though%20some%20of%20the%20efforts%20at%20home%20appear%20to%20be%20working%2C%20as%20deaths%20from%20fentanyl%20overdoses%20are%20finally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dea.gov%2Fpress-releases%2F2024%2F11%2F15%2Fdeas-third-annual-national-family-summit-fentanyl-highlights-progress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20decline%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221402%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20member%20of%20U.S.%20Naval%20Special%20Warfare%20Task%20Unit%20Europe%20(NSWTU-E)%20provides%20cover%20during%20a%20raid%20with%20Cypriot%20Army%20Special%20Forces%20in%20Cyprus%2C%20September%2028%2C%202021.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6610bc1616bde8d4ead6530e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22934%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20member%20of%20US%20Naval%20Special%20Warfare%20Task%20Unit%20Europe%20(NSWTU-E)%20provides%20cover%20during%20a%20raid%20with%20foreign%20special%20operations%20forces.%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Army%20Photo%20by%20Sgt.%20Patrik%20Orcutt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20special%20operations%20is%20much%20smaller%20than%20conventional%20military%20forces%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20isn't%20designed%20to%20solve%20every%20problem%20that%20might%20warrant%20military%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20public%20imagination%2C%20SOF%20is%20not%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%20engaged%20in%20the%20kinds%20of%20operations%20that%20people%20often%20imagine%2C%20that%20are%20depicted%20in%20Hollywood%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoffman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20engaged%20in%20less%20glamorous%20things%20like%20training%20indigenous%20forces%2C%20gathering%20intelligence%2C%20psychological%20operations%2C%20%5Band%5D%20civil%20affairs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBolstering%20Mexico's%20internal%20defenses%20could%20be%20a%20worthwhile%20endeavor%2C%20the%20active-duty%20special%20operator%20told%20BI%2C%20but%20prioritizing%20military%20intervention%20over%20non-violent%20approaches%2C%20like%20empowering%20the%20State%20and%20Treasury%20departments%20to%20apply%20pressure%20on%20the%20financial%20institutions%20used%20by%20cartels%2C%20would%20be%20foolhardy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dbf845de-822b-41b8-979d-938e48c184e1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20dangers%20of%20getting%20it%20wrong%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EViolence%20against%20cartels%20could%20trigger%20a%20humanitarian%20crisis%20and%20spur%20more%20immigration%20to%20the%20US%2C%20said%20Guadalupe%20Correa-Cabrera%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20George%20Mason%20University%20who%20has%20extensively%20studied%20cartels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMexican%20civilians%20caught%20in%20the%20crossfire%20would%20likely%20flee%20communities%2C%20which%20could%20create%20a%20refugee%20crisis%2C%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20going%20to%20apply%20for%20asylum%20in%20a%20desperate%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20calling%20the%20idea%20of%20immediate%20military%20intervention%20illogical.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20as%20simple%20as%20killing%20top%20leaders%20either.%20Complicating%20the%20grip%20cartels%20have%20on%20Mexican%20society%20is%20their%20seemingly%20infinite%20complexity%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20talking%20about%20businesses%20that%20operate%20vertically%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsinaloa-cartel-doing-well-5-years-after-el-chapo-caught-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEl%20Chapo%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-ups-reward-for-sinaloa-leaders-war-brews-within-cartel-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEl%20Mayo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20all%20these%20guys%20that%20provide%20orders%20to%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20two%20infamous%20drug%20kingpins.%20Most%20cartels%20operate%20with%20less%20centralized%20command%20structures%20and%20are%20splintered%20into%20smaller%20cells.%20Some%20of%20these%20focus%20on%20drug%20movements%20and%20production%2C%20while%20others%20focus%20on%20kidnapping%2C%20extortion%2C%20and%20human%20smuggling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20limit%20the%20reach%20of%20the%20cartels%20and%20the%20violence%20and%20the%20destruction%20that%20comes%20with%20them%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20are%20going%20to%20get%20the%20exact%20opposite%20effect%26quot%3B%20if%20you%20start%20killing%20leaders%2C%20said%20Carolyn%20Gallaher%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20American%20University%20who%20studies%20cartels%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETop%20leaders%20can%20be%20easily%20replaced%20by%20others%20zealously%20vying%20for%20power%2C%20creating%20an%20even%20more%20complex%20battlefield%20for%20American%20troops%20and%20Mexican%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20start%20fighting%20an%20army%20that%20is%20not%20behaving%20like%20a%20regular%20military%2C%20you%20are%20basically%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20civilian%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Gallaher%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you%20don't%20have%20an%20accurate%20way%20to%20differentiate%20between%20civilian%20and%20soldier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20special%20operations%20mortar%20Syria%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61a6295b1f8b8c00195acf0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECoalition%20and%20Anti-Terror%20Forces%20fire%20mortar%20rounds%20on%20an%20overseas%20live-fire%20range.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%2FSgt.%20Brandon%20White%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDoug%20Livermore%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20Special%20Operations%20Association%20of%20America%20and%20a%20senior%20Green%20Beret%20officer%20in%20the%20National%20Guard%20who%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atlanticcouncil.org%2Fblogs%2Fnew-atlanticist%2Fus-intervention-against-mexican-cartels-carries-major-risks-heres-how-to-mitigate-them%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewritten%20about%20narcoterrorism%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20special%20operations%20is%20just%20one%20tool%20in%20the%20vast%20US%20government%20toolbox%2C%20and%20can't%20be%20the%20main%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20military%20approach%20by%20itself%20will%20not%20be%20sufficient.%20It%20will%20not%20solve%20the%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Livermore%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20suggested%20a%20broader%20approach%20involving%20US%20special%20operations-provided%20intelligence%20or%20efforts%20to%20bolster%20internal%20security.%20However%2C%20Livermore%20said%20rampant%20corruption%20in%20Mexico's%20government%20agencies%C2%A0could%20complicate%20these%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20recommended%20a%20closer%20examination%20and%20targeting%20of%20China's%20role%20in%20the%20US%20drug%20crisis%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20supply%20of%20chemical%20and%20financial%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fopa%2Fpr%2Fchina-based-chemical-manufacturing-companies-and-employees-indicted-alleged-fentanyl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%20to%20cartels%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20what%20endstates%20the%20Trump%20administration%20desires%20to%20achieve%20to%20define%20success%2C%20said%20the%20SOF%20operator.%20Lacking%20such%20parameters%20could%20lead%20to%20another%20quagmire.%20It%20seems%20likely%2C%20however%2C%20that%20any%20effective%20operation%20to%20dismantle%20them%20will%20take%20years%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20done%20in%20a%20short%20amount%20of%20time%3B%20it%20takes%20consistent%20effort%20and%20partnership%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20operator%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20take%20a%20generation%20or%20two%3B%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20done%20in%20four%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-sending-special-operators-confront-cartels-risky-play-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737808202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6794007e196626c40984fe44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-sending-special-operators-confront-cartels-risky-play-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There's%20a%20potential%20role%20for%20special%20operations%20forces%20in%20combating%20cartels%2C%20but%20getting%20this%20wrong%20could%20up%20create%20more%20problems.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbaker%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A286%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-sending-special-operators-confront-cartels-risky-play-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IDFC%20First%20Bank%20Q3FY25%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20falls%2053%25%20to%20Rs%20339%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737808158000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fidfc-first-bank-q3fy25-results-