ering%20perhaps%20one%20pregnancy%2C%20but%2C%20like%20her%20sister%2C%20she%20believes%20adoption%20is%20her%20best%20course%20to%20parenthood.%20However%2C%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flgbtq-figures-you-should-know-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELGBTQ%2B%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20also%20recognizes%20that%20motherhood%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20through%20a%20biological%20child%2C%20adoption%2C%20or%20a%20combination%20of%20the%20two%20%E2%80%94%20could%20be%20out%20of%20reach%20due%20to%20expense%20and%20possible%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20leaves%20me%20with%20one%20child%20who%20seems%20content%2C%20at%20least%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20to%20pursue%20having%20a%20family%20%26quot%3Bthe%20old-fashioned%20way%20eventually.%26quot%3B%20She%20and%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcall-my-boyfriend-partner-controversial-relationship-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esignificant%20other%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20have%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20before%20kids%20are%20even%20glimmers%20in%20their%20respective%20eyes.%20They're%20pursuing%20careers%20in%20highly%20competitive%20fields%2C%20which%20won't%20allow%20time%20to%20grow%20a%20family%20for%20several%20of%20their%20most%20fertile%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20children%20are%20far%20from%20alone.%20According%20to%20the%20CDC%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fnchs%2Fpressroom%2Fnchs_press_releases%2F2024%2F20240525.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20birth%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20decreased%20by%202%25%20annually%20over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20reaching%20a%20historic%20low%20in%202023.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fsocial-trends%2F2024%2F07%2F25%2Fthe-experiences-of-u-s-adults-who-dont-have-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPew%20Research%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20adults%20under