4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20learning%20to%20accept%20and%20support%20my%20daughters'%20decisions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAsk%20any%20grammy%20or%20grandad%2C%20and%20they'll%20tell%20you%20the%20payoff%20for%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20raising%20those%20helpless%20humans%20into%20productive%20citizens%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffine-not-becoming-grandparent-sons-dont-have-kids-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egift%20of%20grandparenthood%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20thought%20of%20possibly%20never%20receiving%20this%20well-deserved%20prize%20makes%20me%20feel%20rather%20sorry%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20realize%20my%20children%20don't%20owe%20me%20anything%2C%20and%20honestly%2C%20the%20joys%20of%20watching%20them%20grow%20into%20the%20amazing%20young%20women%20they've%20become%20have%20truly%20been%20the%20greatest%20gift%20of%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20while%20I%20may%20be%20privately%20nursing%20my%20wounded%20soul%20over%20my%20%26quot%3Blost%26quot%3B%20grandchildren%2C%20I%20know%20I'll%20also%20find%20the%20strength%20to%20support%20my%20kids'%20very%20personal%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdevastated-might-not-be-grandmother-childless-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737806821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67900bf7ae09223df2bae2bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdevastated-might-not-be-grandmother-childless-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22All%20three%20of%20my%20daughters%20have%20decided%20to%20wait%20several%20years%20to%20be%20mothers.%20I%20feel%20sorry%20for%20myself%20that%20I%20won't%20get%20to%20be%20a%20grandmother%20anytime%20soon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(%20Lynnette%20Lyons)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdevastated-might-not-be-grandmother-childless-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump's%20controversial%20pick%20for%20defence%20secretary%20confirmed%20after%20Vance%20casts%20tie-breaking%20vote%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737805800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F01%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-pete-hegseth-senate_6799620.jpg%3F20250114222008%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpete-hegseth-confirmed-as-donald-trumps-defence-secretary-13296014%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pete%20Hegseth%2C%20Donald%20Trump's%20controversial%20choice%20for%20US%20defence%20secretary%2C%20has%20been%20confirmed%20for%20the%20job.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A331%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpete-hegseth-confirmed-as-donald-trumps-defence-secretary-13296014%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fpete-hegseth-confirmed-as-donald-trumps-defence-secretary-13296014%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fpete-hegseth-confirmed-as-donald-trumps-defence-secretary-13296014%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ownership%20Rights%20To%20Refugee%20Colonies%2C%2050%2C000%20Jobs%3A%20BJP's%20Delhi%20Poll%20Promise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Saturday%20launched%20the%20third%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20scheduled%20for%20February%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20announced%20several%20promises%2C%20ranging%20from%20granting%20ownership%20rights%20to%20people%20in%20refugee%20colonies%20to%20reopening%2013%2C000%20sealed%20shops%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20event%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BModi%20ji%20has%20announced%20the%20granting%20of%20ownership%20rights%20to%20more%20than%201%2C700%20unauthorized%20colonies.%20Previously%2C%20these%20colonies%20did%20not%20have%20permission%20for%20construction%2C%20buying%2C%20or%20selling.%20Now%2C%20by%20granting%20them%20full%20ownership%20rights%20and%20aligning%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Housing's%20regulations%20and%20Delhi's%20by-laws%2C%20we%20will%20give%20them%20the%20right%20to%20construct%20and%20sell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B13%2C000%20shops%20in%20Delhi%20are%20sealed%2C%20and%20we%20have%20worked%20with%20lawyers%20to%20find%20a%20legal%20path%20to%20reopen%20them.%20We%20will%20create%20a%20judicial%20authority%20and%20reopen%20these%20shops%20within%20six%20months%20to%20resume%20operations.%20Refugee%20colonies%20that%20have%20been%20established%20since%201947%2C%20such%20as%20Rajendra%20Nagar%2C%20Lajpat%20Nagar%2C%20and%20Kingsway%20Camp%2C%20currently%20have%20people%20on%20lease%3B%20they%20cannot%20sell%20or%20buy%20the%20land.%20We%20will%20grant%20ownership%20rights%20to%20all%20these%20refugees%20who%20have%20land%20on%20lease%20in%20these%20colonies%20in%20the%20first%20Cabinet%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20also%20announced%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20Workers%20Welfare%20Board%20in%20Delhi%2C%20which%20will%20ensure%20that%20all%20workers%20have%20life%20insurance%20coverage%20of%20up%20to%2010%20lakh%20and%20accident%20insurance%20of%20up%20to%205%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20apply%20the%20same%20formula%20for%20textile%20workers.%20We%20will%20provide%20Rs%2010%2C000%20as%20assistance%20to%20workers%2C%20and%20for%20registered%20workers%2C%20we%20will%20offer%20loans%20up%20to%203%20lakh%20to%20enhance%20skills%20and%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20highlighted%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20provide%2050%2C000%20government%20jobs%20to%20the%20youth%20of%20Delhi%20without%20any%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20by%20creating%2020%20lakh%20self-employment%20opportunities%2C%20we%20will%20help%20the%20youth%20find%20employment.%20Through%20an%20investment%20of%2020%2C000%20crore%2C%20we%20will%20develop%20an%20integrated%20public%20transport%20network%20and%20convert%2013%2C000%20buses%20into%20electric%20buses%2C%20making%20Delhi%20a%20100%25%20electric%20bus%20city%20under%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20underlined%20that%20to%20promote%20tourism%2C%20they%20will%20collaborate%20with%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana%20governments%20to%20create%20a%20Mahabharata%20corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20develop%20the%20Yamuna%20Riverfront%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20Sabarmati%20Riverfront.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20invite%20Kejriwal%20to%20join%20us%20after%203%20years%20of%20our%20government%20to%20take%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20Yamuna%20with%20his%20family.%20We%20will%20end%20manual%20scavenging%20100%25%20and%20eliminate%20this%20inhumane%20practice%20completely%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20also%20recalled%20the%20BJP's%20promises%20from%20its%20earlier%20two%20manifestos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20every%20pregnant%20woman%2C%20we%20will%20provide%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs%2012%2C000%20and%20give%20six%20nutrition%20kits.%20LPG%20cylinders%20will%20be%20available%20for%20Rs%20500%2C%20and%20BJP%20will%20provide%20one%20free%20LPG%20cylinder%20to%20every%20sister%20on%20Holi%20and%20Diwali.%20Under%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%2C%20we%20will%20provide%20free%20treatment%20up%20to%205%20lakh%20in%20the%20first%20Cabinet%20meeting%20to%20every%20poor%20person.%20Any%20treatment%20beyond%205%20lakh%20will%20be%20covered%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20ensuring%20that%20every%20poor%20person%20in%20Delhi%20receives%20treatment%20up%20to%2010%20lakh%20at%20no%20cost%2C%20even%20at%20major%20hospitals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20would%20increase%20the%20pension%20for%20senior%20citizens%20from%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20women's%20welfare%2C%20we%20will%20increase%20the%20pension%20for%20widows%20and%20destitute%20women%20from%202%2C500%20Rs%20to%203%2C000%20Rs%20per%20month.%20We%20will%20establish%20Atal%20Canteens%20in%20JJ%20Clusters%2C%20providing%20nutritious%20meals%20for%20just%20Rs%205%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20give%20a%20corruption-free%20and%20transparent%20state%20government.%20Scheduled%20caste%20and%20scheduled%20tribe%20students%20will%20receive%201%2C000%20Rs%20per%20month%20under%20the%20Ambedkar%20Stipend%20Scheme.%20Auto%20and%20taxi%20drivers%20will%20receive%2010%20lakh%20life%20insurance%20and%205%20lakh%20accident%20insurance.%20A%20welfare%20board%20will%20be%20set%20up%20for%20domestic%20workers%2C%20and%20we%20will%20provide%20six%20months%20of%20paid%20maternity%20leave%20to%20mothers.%20We%20will%20double%20the%20PM%20Swanidhi%20scheme%20and%20provide%20financial%20aid%20to%20street%20vendors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20assembly%20elections%20will%20take%20place%20in%20a%20single%20phase%20on%20February%205.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20happen%20on%20February%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-way%20contest%20is%20expected%20in%20Delhi%20between%20the%20ruling%20AAP%2C%20BJP%2C%20and%20Congress.%20AAP%20dominated%20the%202020%20assembly%20elections%20by%20winning%2062%20out%20of%2070%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20secured%20eight%20seats.%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20in%20power%20for%2015%20consecutive%20years%20in%20Delhi%2C%20has%20suffered%20setbacks%20in%20the%20last%20two%20assembly%20elections%20and%20has%20failed%20to%20win%20any%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20s