%20on%20collective%20contribution%2C%20building%20supportive%20communities%2C%20and%20dismantling%20existing%20structures%20that%20perpetuate%20violence%20and%20inequity.%20We%20are%20learning%20that%20women%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20not%20only%20empowers%20women%20and%20girls%20but%20also%20all%20marginalised%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20over%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20Navchetana%20Sarvangin%20Vikas%20Kendra%2C%20led%20by%20Manisha%20Sitaram%20Ghule%2C%20has%20made%20a%20profound%20impact.%20Operating%20in%20the%20drought-prone%20Beed%20district%2C%20the%20organisation%20focuses%20on%20advocacy%20for%20land%20rights%20and%20menstrual%20health%20for%20vulnerable%20nomadic%20and%20de-notified%20tribes%2C%20and%20Dalit%20communities.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20they%20have%20enabled%20over%20Rs%20100%20crore%20in%20loans%20from%20banks%2C%20helping%20women%20members%20build%20sustainable%20livelihoods.%20Their%20community%20dairy%20initiative%20is%20enabling%20enhanced%20incomes%2C%20ending%20migration%20for%20work%2C%20and%20bettering%20nutritional%20outcomes%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20512px)%20100vw%2C%20512px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-2-1737634010.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manisha%20Sitaram%20Ghule%20started%20a%20dairy%20initiative%20in%20Beed%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-2-1737634010.jpg%20512w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-2-1737634010-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-2-1737634010-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-2-1737634010-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterin