0infrastructure%20but%20also%20deny%20women%20access%20to%20stable%20livelihoods%2C%20social%20support%2C%20and%20dignity%2C%20reinforcing%20cycles%20of%20poverty%20and%20exclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20rural%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20Bandana%2C%20faced%20the%20challenge%20of%20navigating%20life%20without%20a%20partner%2C%20securing%20entitlements%20like%20widow%20pensions%2C%20while%20regaining%20financial%20independence.%20Her%20personal%20struggle%20revealed%20to%20her%20the%20harsher%20realities%20for%20widows%20from%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20who%20are%20often%20left%20voiceless%20and%20invisible.%20While%20she%20did%20not%20take%20the%20widow%20pension%20for%20herself%20or%20adopt%20the%20traditional%20identity%20and%20appearance-related%20norms%20around%20widowhood%2C%20she%20fights%20to%20ensure%20other%20widows%20receive%20the%20pension%20and%20support%20they%20deserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20341px)%20100vw%2C%20341px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-3-1737634052.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22341%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bandana%20is%20tackling%20societal%20taboos%20around%20widowhood%20and%20remarriage%20through%20Aakanksha%20Seva%20Sadan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-3-1737634052.jpg%20341w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-3-1737634052-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Funnamed-3-1737634052-150x225.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-400234%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAakanksha%20Seva%20Sadan%20started%20by%20Bandana%20advocates%20for%20access%20to%20social%20services%20and%20challenges%20societal%20taboos%20around%20widowhood%20and%20remarriage%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%