E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Jhili%20was%20able%20to%20monitor%20her%20second%20pregnancy%20closely%20without%20the%20financial%20strain.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20Ganjam%20District%20Administration%E2%80%99s%20initiative%2C%20she%20was%20offered%20up%20to%20three%20ultrasound%20scans%20for%20free%20of%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-2-1737031940.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20ASHA%20worker%20informing%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20about%20the%20free%20ultrasound%20services%20launched%20by%20the%20district%20administration.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-2-1737031940.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-2-1737031940-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-2-1737031940-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-2-1737031940-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-2-1737031940-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-398459%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAn%20ASHA%20worker%20informing%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20about%20the%20free%20ultrasound%20services%20launched%20by%20the%20district%20administration.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20ASHA%20%5BAccredited%20Social%20Health%20Activist%5D%20%3Cem%3Edidi%20%3C%2Fem%3Etold%20me%20that%20it%20is%20for%20free%2C%20I